data.description:
Discover the charm of this 3 bed, 2 full bath sanctuary in the coveted Marine Creek Ranch community. Recently updated with plush new carpeting, this inviting home exudes comfort and warmth.
Entertain effortlessly in the open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area, where natural light accentuates the spacious layout. The updated kitchen boasts granite countertops, a gas stove, an island, and a walk-in pantry.
With flat screen and surround sound wiring pre-installed, you can effortlessly host memorable gatherings. Outside, the family-centric neighborhood offers a community pool, garden, and playground, perfect for creating cherished moments with loved ones.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting haven yours. Schedule a viewing today and embrace the joys of Marine Creek Ranch living.
